maybe the proverbial newbie is using the graphical interface provided by 
help.start() (maybe through RStudio) and choosing the 'Search Engine & Keywords' 
link, where entering findOverlaps returns something approximating helpful (man 
pages on which findOverlaps methods are defined, Herv?'s suggestion, I think, 
though for installed rather than loaded packages) whereas entering length does 
not (man pages on which length is defined, but there are too many man pages! 
