methods is not too overwhelming (well, moderately overwhelming; is my 'GRanges' 
a 'GenomiceRanges' or a 'Ranges' or an 'ANY'??). Of course a more automatic 
solution would be great, or in lieu of that the careful manual curation 
suggested by the original post / realized by Herv?.

