Subject: [Bioc-devel] A quick check for matching seqnames/order needed
 for Views on RleList?
In-Reply-To: <CAC2h7uvvM6390SFgJxy+_Ao3XPU5vJ+jKFXRG4Fu85MV-Z8dUw@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CANeAVBmwK=vSz0+m31RyiuC8htu3PxiHt1oCsU4Cb+x8UXUEqQ@mail.gmail.com>	<CADfHdv4foCGZprsU1HhRodBEcZQTXRRi7WXaaO=mY_7HXQ4uBw@mail.gmail.com>	<CANeAVBn1JqakmHN8W0taX4ojTEGksu_areBbh-vQv5euAzWTug@mail.gmail.com>
